<html>
<head>
<title>Termcast</title>
<link href="static/styles/viewer.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
<script src="static/js/jquery-1.4.1.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<img src="../static/images/termcast_logo_web.png" width="265" height="120" alt="termcast logo" />
<hr />
[% IF stream_data.keys.size %]
<p>The following sessions are in progress:</p>
<ul>
[% FOREACH stream_id = stream_data.keys %]
[% NEXT UNLESS stream_data.$stream_id.object %]
<li>

    <strong><a href="tv/[% stream_id %]">[% stream_data.$stream_id.object.username %]</a></strong>

    - idle <span class="idle">[% stream_data.$stream_id.idle %]</span>

    - <span class="viewers">[% stream_data.$stream_id.viewers %]</span> viewers

</li>

[% END %]
</ul>
[% ELSE %]
Nobody is streaming at this time.
[% END %]

<hr />

<p>
    To stream, follow these instructions:

    <pre style="background-color: white; border: solid 1px black; width: 600px">
    git clone git://github.com/jasonmay/app-termcast.git
    cd app-termcast
    perl -Ilib bin/termcast --host jarsonmar.org
    </pre>
    This is just a fork of doy's App::Termcast but my fork is the only client that will work on my server (for custom term geometry). Not merging until I am happy with my implementation. Sorry!
</p>
</body>
</html>
